{"tid":848272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩節目咁好品味介紹淡水魚生","createTime":"2018-10-04T20:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T16:31:02.000Z","uid":66324,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"228241e6ef8515c06c2ec34a8053fc4c44621ba8","tid":848272,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T20:12:36.000Z","msg":"&quot;食物安全中心 Centre for Food Safety<br />\n<br />\n切勿進食淡水魚生<br />\n<br />\n最近有電視節目介紹用<span style=\"color: red;\">鯇魚</span>製作魚生，引起關注。<br />\n<br />\n在一般環境下飼養的淡水魚(例如鯇魚及大頭魚)，除了致病菌外，還可能帶有寄生蟲，例如可造成膽管梗阻、肝硬化和引致膽管癌的中華肝吸蟲。酒、醋、日式芥辣、黃芥辣及香料均不能殺死包括中華肝吸蟲在內的寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n市民無論是在港或外遊，切勿進食生或未徹底煮熟的淡水魚。在吃火鍋或粥品時，須待魚熟透方可進食。為保障公眾健康，根據《食物業規例》(第132X章)，本港禁售中式魚生。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n食物安全焦點 -- 淡水魚生中的中華肝吸蟲&quot;<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線生食鯇魚同自殺有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce157c0df7aeefa22a694ed666c4bacb0bfc737a","tid":848272,"uid":100136,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T23:45:58.000Z","msg":"電視節目就唔知嘞<br />\n我淨係知西DorSi有食過啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31a5a5d7fd4abd449d35916b8fddd5adceb6bcb","tid":848272,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T00:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db555049dafbe631ad9b71fe852f8e5ec044f41a","tid":848272,"uid":6111,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ce157c0df7aeefa22a694ed666c4bacb0bfc737a","tid":848272,"uid":100136,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T23:45:58.000Z","msg":"電視節目就唔知嘞<br />\n我淨係知西DorSi有食過啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣唔死都冇乜用架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75000b306974a4321068ce295a366ce496f49028","tid":848272,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2381dddc6d44f0c39eac959895a07e9d1f6e971f","tid":848272,"uid":212213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"魚樂無窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de32058bbfa73e8cae4975dd2ec8c8cf26519b3","tid":848272,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"上得大灣區都係水魚，水魚食魚生有乜問題"},{"pid":"af11337ea09271ccb8c5bdb155c2cdafae970708","tid":848272,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9de32058bbfa73e8cae4975dd2ec8c8cf26519b3","tid":848272,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"上得大灣區都係水魚，水魚食魚生有乜問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"你自己私人食就無問題, 自己柒姐, 而家上埋電視節目真係不得了"},{"pid":"b8bbbce3f1e441086fe5b61492556c3bcfb4f239","tid":848272,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中華肝吸蟲 </strong></span></span>"}]}